---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Services"
  description="Halliday helps nonprofits turn disconnected data into smarter decisions through a three-stage value chain: Impact Data Review, Strategic Advisory, and Custom Solutions."
>
  <!-- Page header -->
  <section class="bg-[var(--color-primary-dark)] text-white py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-[var(--color-accent)] font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">
          Services
        </p>
        <h1
          class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6"
          style="font-family: var(--font-heading);"
        >
          How We Work With Nonprofits
        </h1>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-xl leading-relaxed">
          Every engagement starts with understanding what your data can already tell you. Where it goes from there depends on what you need.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stage 1: Impact Data Review -->
  <section id="impact-data-review" class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-[var(--color-surface)]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div data-animate>
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-[var(--color-primary)]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[var(--color-primary)] mb-6">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-accent)] font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Stage 1</p>
          <h2
            class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-3"
            style="font-family: var(--font-heading);"
          >
            Impact Data Review
          </h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-lg font-medium mb-5">See what your data is already trying to tell you.</p>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Before we recommend anything, we look at what you have. The Impact Data Review is a fixed-scope engagement where we analyze your existing data — donor records, program metrics, financial data — and deliver a clear, visual report showing what your data is actually saying.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-base leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Most nonprofits are surprised by what's already in their data. The IDR surfaces patterns you haven't seen — donor retention trends, at-risk supporters, program effectiveness signals — and gives you a foundation for every decision that follows.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[var(--color-accent)] hover:bg-[var(--color-accent-hover)] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold transition-colors"
          >
            Start Your Impact Data Review
          </a>
        </div>

        <div data-animate data-animate-delay="200">
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            {[
              'Fixed scope, fixed timeline',
              'Delivered as a polished visual report designed for leadership',
              'Typically completed in 2–3 weeks',
              'No new systems to implement, no technical prerequisites',
            ].map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-primary)]/10 flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3 w-3 text-[var(--color-primary)]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-sm leading-relaxed">{item}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stage 2: Strategic Advisory -->
  <section id="strategic-advisory" class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-[var(--color-background)]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1" data-animate data-animate-delay="200">
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            {[
              'Ongoing advisory retainers or project-based engagements',
              'Tool evaluation, vendor assessment, implementation planning',
              'Designed to augment your existing team, not replace it',
            ].map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-primary)]/10 flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3 w-3 text-[var(--color-primary)]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-sm leading-relaxed">{item}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2" data-animate>
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-[var(--color-primary)]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[var(--color-primary)] mb-6">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 12l3-3 3 3 4-4M8 21l4-4 4 4M3 4h18M4 4h16v12a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V4z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-accent)] font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Stage 2</p>
          <h2
            class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-3"
            style="font-family: var(--font-heading);"
          >
            Strategic Advisory
          </h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-lg font-medium mb-5">Turn insights into a plan you can actually execute.</p>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Once you can see the picture, the question becomes: what do you do about it? We help nonprofit leadership translate data insights into operational decisions — which tools to adopt, which processes to fix, where to invest limited resources for maximum impact.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-base leading-relaxed mb-8">
            This is where we help you figure out whether an off-the-shelf tool solves your problem or whether you need something purpose-built. We're technology-agnostic — we'll recommend a $50/month SaaS product if that's the right answer, or scope a custom solution if it's not.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[var(--color-accent)] hover:bg-[var(--color-accent-hover)] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold transition-colors"
          >
            Let's Talk About Your Roadmap
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stage 3: Custom Solutions -->
  <section id="custom-solutions" class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-[var(--color-surface)]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div data-animate>
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-[var(--color-primary)]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[var(--color-primary)] mb-6">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-accent)] font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Stage 3</p>
          <h2
            class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-3"
            style="font-family: var(--font-heading);"
          >
            Custom Solutions
          </h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-lg font-medium mb-5">When the right tool doesn't exist, we build it.</p>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Some problems don't have a product on the shelf. When a nonprofit needs a donor intelligence dashboard that connects to QuickBooks, a program tracking system built around a specific logic model, or an integration between systems that don't talk to each other — we build it.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-base leading-relaxed mb-8">
            We specialize in lightweight, purpose-built tools that do one thing well. No enterprise software bloat. No six-month implementations. Just the right tool for the specific job.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[var(--color-accent)] hover:bg-[var(--color-accent-hover)] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold transition-colors"
          >
            Explore Custom Solutions
          </a>
        </div>

        <div data-animate data-animate-delay="200">
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            {[
              'Custom dashboards and data products',
              'System integrations and automated workflows',
              'Signal by Halliday: donor intelligence powered by your existing QuickBooks data (coming soon)',
            ].map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-primary)]/10 flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3 w-3 text-[var(--color-primary)]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-sm leading-relaxed">{item}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-[var(--color-primary-dark)] text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center" data-animate>
      <h2
        class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-5"
        style="font-family: var(--font-heading);"
      >
        Not sure which stage you're at?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-white/70 text-lg mb-8">
        Most clients start with an Impact Data Review. It's the fastest way to see what your data can tell you — and it gives us both a foundation for deciding what comes next.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-[var(--color-accent)] hover:bg-[var(--color-accent-hover)] text-white px-7 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold transition-colors"
        >
          Book a 30-Minute Intro Call
        </a>
        <a
          href="/assessment"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 border-2 border-white/40 hover:border-white text-white px-7 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-white/10"
        >
          Take the AI Readiness Assessment
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
